title: Windows 10 Insider Preview build 10166 en-US .ESD murphy78
description:
This is a Fast Ring officially published MS build. These esd
files are encrypted and in non-iso format so you need to run
the decrypt script and point it at the appropriate file.
Example:
"decrypt longesdfilename.esd"

Alternatively, put esd file in same folder as the decrypt.cmd
script and drag esd file onto script icon. It should then open
the script and ask for elevation permissions, etc.

RTM won't be signed off til Jul22-24, so if you're holding
out, it'll be a while.
